content: I'm guessin' that if we can make some wishes out of airplanes, then maybe, oh maybe, I'll go back to the days before the politics that we call the rap game, and back when ain't nobody listened to my mixtape. So can I get a wish to end the politics, and get back to the music that started this...? So here I stand, and then again I say - I'm hoping we can make some wishes out of airplanes.
author: B.o.B
